# ===== CART API TESTS =====

### Get Cart (fetch user's cart)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Cookie: token={{token}}

### Add Item to Cart (requires valid productId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{token}}

{
    "productId": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
    "quantity": 2
}

### Update Cart Item Quantity (requires valid itemId from cart)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/item/ITEM_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{token}}

{
    "quantity": 5
}

### Remove Item from Cart (requires valid itemId from cart)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/item/ITEM_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Cookie: token={{token}}

### Clear Entire Cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Cookie: token={{token}}

### Checkout and Create Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{token}}

